    <h3 itemprop="headline">NYC schools track bathroom time with digital hall passes</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      New York City public schools are rolling out SmartPass, a digital hall pass system that tracks student movement, sparking privacy concerns.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/03/nyc-schools-track-bathroom-time-digital-hall-passes/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
