    <h3 itemprop="headline">How to opt out of AI data collection in popular apps</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Most AI platforms use your conversations to train their systems by default. Learn how to turn off data collection on ChatGPT, Google, Alexa and Siri.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/04/how-to-opt-out-ai-data-collection-popular-apps/"  >(Fox News)</a>
