    <h3 itemprop="headline">Canada's Artemis II astronaut gives thumbs-up to 'Project Hail Mary' starring Canadian Ryan Gosling</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The new space movie “Project Hail Mary” starring Ryan Gosling is getting rave reviews more than halfway to the moon.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/04/canadas-artemis-ii-astronaut-gives-thumbs-up-to-project-hail-mary-starring-canadian-ryan-gosling/"  >(Marcia Dunn, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
