        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Cloudflare&#8217;s new CMS is not a WordPress killer, it&#8217;s a WordPress alternative</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Cloudflare on Wednesday rolled out EmDash, which it described as “the spiritual successor to WordPress.” The security vendor positioned EmDash as a far more secure site building tool that avoids the extensive cybersecurity problems with WordPress plugins.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/03/cloudflares-new-cms-is-not-a-wordpress-killer-its-a-wordpress-alternative/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
