        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Nvidia&#8217;s SchedMD acquisition puts open-source AI scheduling under scrutiny</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Nvidia’s recent acquisition of SchedMD, the company behind the Slurm workload manager, is raising concerns among AI industry executives and supercomputing specialists who fear the chip giant could use its new position to favour its own hardware over competing chips, whether through code prioritizati
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/07/nvidias-schedmd-acquisition-puts-open-source-ai-scheduling-under-scrutiny-2/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
