        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Only Trump knows why he replaced Bondi as attorney general, new leader of Justice Department says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Justice Department’s new leader says “nobody” except President Donald Trump knows why Pam Bondi was replaced as attorney general last week.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/07/only-trump-knows-why-he-replaced-bondi-as-attorney-general-new-leader-of-justice-department-says/"  >(Eric Tucker, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
