    <meta itemprop="name" content="Cathy Wurzer and Lukas Levin, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/02/trump-voter-list-isnt-feasible-according-to-top-minnesota-election-official.webp" alt="Top MN election official: Voter list isn't feasible" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Top MN election official: Voter list isn't feasible</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A new executive order directs the Department of Homeland Security and U.S. Postal Service to work with each other to develop a list of eligible voters and only mail ballots to them.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/02/trump-voter-list-isnt-feasible-according-to-top-minnesota-election-official/"  >(Cathy Wurzer and Lukas Levin, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 07 Apr 2026 16:35:46 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 07 Apr 2026 16:35:46 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/07/ex-trump-ally-marjorie-taylor-greene-joins-left-wing-calls-25th-amendment-iran-deadline-nears.webp" alt="Ex-Trump ally Marjorie Taylor Greene joins left-wing calls for the 25th amendment as Iran deadline nears" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ex-Trump ally Marjorie Taylor Greene joins left-wing calls for the 25th amendment as Iran deadline nears</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene calls for President Donald Trump&apos;s removal via the 25th Amendment after his Truth Social post threatening Iran&apos;s civilization.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/07/ex-trump-ally-marjorie-taylor-greene-joins-left-wing-calls-25th-amendment-iran-deadline-nears/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset></main>
